{
  "stem": "20575.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was like a Czech name for that, where people got-- but again, how they were treated, if they had medication, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know friends of mine who had encephalitis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to go to the hospital because they were act like, you know, they were out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some died, and some came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Terezin?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the worst thing was, basically, that-- that one day [INAUDIBLE] where we were collected, and we thought we're going to get killed there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody thought.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were standing there with the guns just waiting to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're waiting for from Berlin, and we were told they're waiting for something from Berlin what to do with us, because what are we going to do, like 60,000 people standing around there?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What are they going to do with us?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then like I said, all of a sudden, in the evening, is they're back again, and it was like a horde, all the people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how we found our way back all together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That stands out especially, and of course, saying goodbye to friends who were sent away where we didn't know where they are going.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it went on constantly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still am, I still am.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lives very close by here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was-- I met her in Judenschule in Vienna, because she lived a different place, and I lived in different place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we became best friends when we're 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she also was sent to Terezin, but later, because she got diphtheria in the hospital-- or was it scarlet fever, or whatever-- she got in the camp, so they sent her away.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And her parents and her sister came to Terezin, and she came in January, '93.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
